Well known for her feature on Mobi Dixon's track Bhutiza, vocalist Nichume has died. The Singer is said to have committed suicide last night by jumping off a building in Johannesburg. In a statement released by her record label Top Chap Media this morning it was confirmed that Nichume died from an apparent suicide in her Johannesburg home.  STATEMENT:  I don’t know anybody who hates taking pictures more than me... but sometimes I gotta nigga up and strike a pose ?? Good morning ya’ll ?? It’s a woman crush Wednesday ?? tell somebody how beautiful they are ?? noba uqumbile ?? • • • ?? @masterpic5 A post shared by  Nichume (@nichumesings) on May 14, 2019 at 11:41pm PDT 